{
  "chapter": "055",
  "title": "留侯世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>，他的祖先是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国人。祖父开地，做过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>昭<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>、宣惠<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>、襄哀<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的相。父亲平，做过釐<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩悼惠王\">悼惠王（韩悼惠王）</span>的相。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩悼惠王\">悼惠王（韩悼惠王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>，平去世。父死后<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>〖◈灭<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>当时年少，没有在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>做官。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>家有僮仆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百人</span>，弟弟死了也不安葬，把全部家财拿来寻求<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">刺客<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，为〖◆韩</span>报仇，因为祖父、父亲五代做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>相的缘故。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>曾经在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span>学<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>。东去拜见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仓海君</span>。得到一位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">力士</span>，为他制作<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁椎</span>，重<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百二十斤</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>东巡，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>与刺客在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">博浪沙</span>中埋伏<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>，误中副<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>大怒，大力搜捕<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，追查刺客甚急，就是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>于是改换姓名，逃匿到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邳</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>曾经闲暇时从容地在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邳</span>桥上散步，有一位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">老父</span>，穿着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">褐</span>衣，来到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>身边，故意把他的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">履扔到桥下，回头对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"小子，下去给我把〖•履</span>取上来！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>愕然，想要殴打他。因为他年老，强忍下来，下去取<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">履</span>。老父说：\"给我穿上！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>既然为他取了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">履</span>，就长跪着给他穿上。老父抬脚让他穿，笑着离去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>十分惊异，一直目送他。老父走了一里多地，又折回来，说：\"<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">孺子可教</span>啊。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五天</span>后天亮，与我在这里会面。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>感到奇怪，跪下答道：\"好。\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五天</span>后天亮，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>前往。老父已经先到了，生气地说：\"和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">老人</span>约会，却迟到，为什么？\"离去时说：\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五天</span>后早点来。\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五天</span>后<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸡</span>叫时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>又去。老父又先到了，又生气地说：\"又迟到，为什么？\"离去说：\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五天</span>后再早些来。\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五天</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>半夜就去。过了一会，老父也来了，高兴地说：\"应当这样。\"拿出一本<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>，说：\"读了这个就可以做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>者的老师了。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>后兴盛。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>后你来<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济北</span>见我，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">穀城</span>山下的黄石就是我了。\"说完就离去，没有其他话，不再出现。天亮看那<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>，原来是<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">太公兵法</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>因此认为它非凡，常常学习诵读。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邳</span>，做任侠之事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span>曾经<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人，跟着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>躲藏。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>等起兵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>也聚集<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少年</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景驹</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>代理<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，在留地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>打算前去归附他，半路遇到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邳</span>以西攻城略地，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>于是归属他。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>为厩将。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>多次用<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">太公兵法</span>游说<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公称善，常采用他的计策。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>向其他人讲这些，都不能领会。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公大概是天授之才。\"因此就跟随他，不去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景驹</span>了。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>怀<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>于是劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>说：\"您已立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国后嗣，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>诸<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公子</span>中<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">横阳君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩成\">成（韩成）</span>贤能，可以<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，多树同党。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>去找<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩成</span>，立他为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申徒</span>，和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀人</span>向西攻略<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>地，获得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数座城</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军又夺回，来往于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>一带做游击部队。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>南出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">轘辕</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>率兵跟随<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀城</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨熊</span>军。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公于是命令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王成</span>留守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳翟</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>一起南下，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>，向西进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公想用<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二万人</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>峣关的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">下军</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>劝道：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵还强，不能轻敌。我听说他们的将领是屠夫之子，商贩之人容易被利益打动。希望<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公暂且驻守，派人先行，准备<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五万人</span>的军粮，增加在各山上布<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旗帜</span>，作为疑兵，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦食其</span>拿着贵重<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝</span>物去收买<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将果然叛变，想要联合一起向西袭击<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公想答应。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"这只是其主将想反叛罢了，恐怕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>不听从。不听从必有危险，不如趁其松懈<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>他。\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公于是率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之。向北到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓝田</span>，再战，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">失败</span>。于是到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，秦<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子婴</span>向<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>宫，宫室、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帷帐</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>、贵重<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝</span>物及妇女数以千计，打算留下居住。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>劝<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公搬出，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公不听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>无道，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公才能到此。为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>除去残暴，应当以俭朴为本。如今刚进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>地，就安享其享乐，这就是所说的'助桀为虐'。况且'忠言逆耳利于行，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">毒药</span>苦口利于病'，希望<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公听<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>的话。\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公于是还军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸿门</span>下，打算<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span>就连夜驰入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公军中，私下见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>，想和他一起离开。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"我是为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>送<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公的，如今事态紧急，逃走不合大义。\"于是把情况都告诉了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公大惊，说：\"该怎么办？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公果真想背叛<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>吗？\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公说：\"小人教我守关不让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>入内，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>地就可以全都称王，所以听了他的话。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公自己估量能击退<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>吗？\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公沉默了好久，说：\"当然不能。现在怎么办？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>于是坚决邀请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span>见到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公与他一同饮酒祝寿，结为儿女亲家。让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span>详细说明<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公不敢背叛<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>，所以把守关隘，是为防备其他盗贼。之后见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>而化解了危机，这件事记在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>的事迹中。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉元年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>，统治<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蜀</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>百溢，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">珠</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二斗</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>全都献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>也因此让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>厚赠<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span>，让他请求<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>之地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>便答应了，于是得到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>地。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">前往封国</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>送到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃中</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>返回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>趁机劝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>何不烧毁所经过的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">栈道</span>，向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>表示没有东归的打算，以稳固<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>的心。\"于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>返回。一路上，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">烧</span>毁<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">栈道</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王成</span>因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>跟随过<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>的缘故，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>不让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩成\">成（韩成）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">前往封国</span>，跟着一起东行。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">烧</span>毁了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">栈道</span>，没有东归的心了。\"又用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛的事，用<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">书</span>信告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>因此不担心<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>向西进军，而出兵向北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>竟然不肯让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>归国，只让他做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>，又在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>逃亡，从小路归附<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>也已经回军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>了。又任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">成信侯</span>，跟随向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">失败</span>而回。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邑</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>下<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>靠着马鞍问：\"我想舍弃关以东地区，谁可以与我共建功业？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>进言说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">枭将</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>有嫌隙；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛：这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>可紧急派用。而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>的将领中唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>可委以大事，独当一面。若是要舍弃这些地方，就舍弃给这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>，那么<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>就可以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>了。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>去游说<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>，派人联络<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>。等到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>他，趁势<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。然而最终<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的，就是这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>之力。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>多病，从未单独带过兵，常常为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>筹划策略，时时跟从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>紧急<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>恐惧忧虑，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦食其</span>商议削弱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的权势。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">食其</span>说：\"从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>其后裔于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>其后裔于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>失德弃义，侵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的社稷，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>的后嗣，使他们没有立锥之地。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>若能再立<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>的后代，都接受<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>绶，这样他们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君臣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>必定都感戴<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的恩德，无不向风慕义，愿做您的臣仆。德义已行，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>南面称霸，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>必敛衽来朝。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"好。赶紧刻<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，先生就带着出发吧。\""
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">食其</span>还没有动身，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>从外面进来拜见。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>正在吃饭，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">子房（张良）</span>过来！有人为我谋划削弱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的权势。\"就把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>的话告诉他，说：\"在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">子房（张良）</span>看来怎么样？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"是谁为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>出这个计策？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的大事要完了。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"为什么？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>答道：\"请允许我借您面前的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">箸</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>筹划。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>其后于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>，是估量自己能制<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>的死命。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>能制<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>的死命吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"这是不可行的第一条。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>其后于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，是估量能得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的首级。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>能得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>的首级吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"这是不可行的第二条。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>，表彰<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商容</span>的里门，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">释放</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕子</span>的囚禁，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>的墓。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>能<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣人</span>的墓，表彰<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤者</span>的里门，对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">智者</span>的家门致敬吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"这是不可行的第三条。又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">散发</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜桥</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粮食</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">散发</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鹿台</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱币，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">赐给</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贫穷</span>者。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">散发</span>〖•府库</span>的钱财来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">赐给</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贫穷</span>的人吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"这是不可行的第四条。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的事结束后，把兵车改为乘车，倒置干<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">戈</span>，蒙上<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>皮，向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>表示不再用兵。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>能停止武备而施行文治，不再用兵吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"这是不可行的第五条。把<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>休放于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华山</span>的南面，表示不再有战事。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>能休放<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>不再使用吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"这是不可行的第六条。把<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>放牧在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桃林</span>的北面，表示不再运输积蓄。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>能放牧<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>不再运输积蓄吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>说：\"这是不可行的第七条。况且<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">游士</span>离开他们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>，舍弃坟墓，别离故旧，跟从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>奔走，只是想日夜期待获得一块小小的土地。如今恢复<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>，立起<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的后代，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">游士</span>各自回去侍奉其主，跟随他们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>，回到故旧坟墓，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>与谁去取<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>呢？这是不可行的第八条。况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>若不强大，那被立起的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>势力会再次屈服于他，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>怎么能使他们臣服呢？果真用客人的计谋，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的大事就完了。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>停下进餐，吐出口中的食物，骂道：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">竖儒</span>，几乎败坏了你<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>的大事！\"令赶快销毁<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>玺。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>而想<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>发怒。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>劝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>授给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，这件事记在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴（韩信）</span>的事迹中。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "这年<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">秋</span>天，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>追击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳夏</span>南，战事不利而据守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">固陵</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>约定来会却不到。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>劝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>采用他的计策，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都来了。这件事记在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>的事迹中。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉六年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>赏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>未曾有战斗之功，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语·现代：运筹帷幄\">在帷帐之中运筹（运筹帷幄）</span>，决胜<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之外，这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">子房（张良）</span>的功劳。自己从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地选择<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万户</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>说：\"当初我起兵于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邳</span>，与皇上在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">留</span>地相会，这是上天把我交给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>采用我的计策，侥幸常常应验，我希望<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">留</span>地就够了，不敢承受<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万户</span>。\"于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>，和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>等一起<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>赏。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "皇上已经<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>了大<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀人</span>，其余的人日夜争功无法定夺，无法<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>赏。皇上在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>南宫，从<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">复道</span>望见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>时常聚坐在沙地上说话。皇上说：\"这是在说什么？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>不知道吗？这是谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>啊。\"皇上说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>刚刚安定，为什么要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布</span>衣起家，靠这些人夺取<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，而所<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>都是萧、曹等故交所亲爱的，所<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀的都是平生的仇人。如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军吏</span>计算功劳，因为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之地不够全部<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>赏，这些人害怕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>不能都<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>他们，又怕被追究平生过失而被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，所以聚在一起谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>啊。\"皇上忧虑地说：\"怎么办呢？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"皇上平生所憎恨的，又是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>共知的，谁最甚？\"皇上说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍齿</span>与我有旧怨，多次给我困辱。我想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他，因他功多，不忍。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"现在赶快先<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍齿</span>给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>看，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍齿</span>被<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>，就人人安心了。\"于是皇上便摆<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍齿</span>为什方<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>，并催促<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>评定功劳进行<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>赏。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>酒罢，都高兴地说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍齿</span>尚且被封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>，我们就没什么可忧虑的了。\""
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"应该建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>。\"皇上犹豫不决。左右的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>人，多数劝皇上建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>东有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>，西有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黾</span>，背靠<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，面向<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">伊</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>，险固也足以依靠。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>虽然有这样的险固，但中部狭小，不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百里</span>，田地贫薄，四面受敌，这不是用武之国。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>左有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽函</span>，右有陇<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蜀</span>，沃野<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>，南有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蜀</span>的富饶，北有<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>人牧场之利，凭借三面险阻防守，只以一面向东控制<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>安定时，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>道漕运<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的物资，西供<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>有变时，顺流而下，足以输送军需。这就是所谓的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金城</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>，天府之国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>的建议是对的。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>当天就起驾，向西建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>跟随入关。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>体质多病，就做道引、不吃五谷，闭门不出<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一年多</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "皇上想废除<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>的儿子<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>们多劝谏争执，未能得到皇上坚定的决断。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>恐惧，不知怎么办。有人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>善出奇策，皇上信用他。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>于是派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建成侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕泽</span>胁迫<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>，说：\"您经常做皇上的谋臣，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今上</span>想更换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，您怎么能高枕而卧呢？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"当初皇上多次处于困境时，有幸采用了我的计策。如今<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>安定，凭宠爱想换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，是骨肉之间的事，即使我们<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>又有什么用。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕泽</span>强求说：\"为我出个主意。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"这是用口舌难以争辩的。但有皇上所请不来的人，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>。这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>年纪都老了，都认为皇上轻慢人，所以逃入山中，坚持道义不做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>臣。然而皇上敬重这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>。如今您果真能不吝惜黄金、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">璧</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>写<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>信，辞意谦卑，准备安<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">辩士</span>恳切邀请，他们应当会来。来了以后，让他们做宾客，经常跟随入朝，让皇上看到他们，皇上必定惊异而询问。一问，就知道这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>贤能，这就是一大助力。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕泽</span>派人奉持<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>信，辞卑礼厚，迎请这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>到了，客居在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建成侯</span>那里。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛，皇上有病，想让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>率兵，前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>他。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>相互商量说：\"我们所以来，是为了保全<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>带兵，事情就危险了。\"于是劝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建成侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>带兵，有功则地位不会在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>之上再晋升；无功归来，就要从此受祸了。况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>所带的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>，都是曾与皇上平定<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">枭将</span>，如今让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>统领他们，这无异于让<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span>领<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狼</span>，他们都不肯尽力，无功必定啊。我听说'母亲受宠儿子被抱着'，如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>日夜侍奉，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>常被抱在皇上面前，皇上说'终究不能让不肖之子在爱子之上'，可见他取代<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的地位必定了。您何不赶紧请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>趁机向皇上哭诉说：'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的猛将，善用兵，如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>都是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>从前的同辈，竟让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>统领他们，这无异于让<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span>领<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狼</span>，没人肯为他效力，况且让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>听说后，就会擂鼓而西进。皇上虽然有病，也该勉强乘坐辎<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，躺着统军督战，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>不敢不尽力。皇上虽然辛苦，也为了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>坚强些。'\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕泽</span>当夜见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>趁机向皇上哭诉陈情，按照<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>所说的那样。皇上说：\"我想这小子本来就不堪派遣，还是我<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>自己去吧。\"于是皇上亲自率兵东征，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>留守，都送到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灞上</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>有病，勉强起身，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲邮</span>见皇上说：\"我本应随行，病得厉害。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人剽悍敏捷，希望皇上不要与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人争锋。\"又劝皇上说：\"让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，监护<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>的军队。\"皇上说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">子房（张良）</span>虽然病着，强撑在床辅佐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>吧。\"此时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>代行<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">少傅</span>之职。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉十二年</span>，皇上从<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>的军队归来，病情加重，愈发想更换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>劝谏，皇上不听，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>就称病不理事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span>引证古今，以死力争<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。皇上假意答应，仍想更换。到了宴会上，摆设<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>陪侍。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>跟随<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，年纪都<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八十有馀</span>岁，须眉雪白，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣冠</span>甚为威严。皇上奇怪，问道：\"他们是做什么的？\"<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>上前对答，各自说出名姓，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">东园公</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">角里先生</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">绮里季</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏黄公</span>。皇上大为惊讶，说：\"我寻求<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>们已<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">数年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>们躲避我，如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>们为什么自己跟从我的儿子游处？\"<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>都说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>轻视<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人好谩骂，我们坚持道义不受凌辱，所以害怕而逃匿。私下里听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>为人仁孝，恭敬爱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之人无不伸长脖子愿为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>效死，所以我们就来了。\"皇上说：\"麻烦<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>们最终好好调护<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>吧。\""
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>祝寿完毕，快步退去。皇上目送他们，召来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>指着这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>说：\"我想换掉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，他们<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>辅佐他，羽翼已成，难以动摇了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>真的是你的主人了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>哭泣，皇上说：\"为我跳<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地之舞，我为你唱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地之歌。\"歌词是： \"<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸿鹄</span>高飞，一举<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>。 羽翼已就，横越四海。 横越四海，又能如何！ 虽有弓矢带绳，又向哪里施射！\" 歌了几遍，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>抽泣流泪，皇上起身离去，散了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>宴。终究没有更换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，根本上是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>招来这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>的功劳。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>跟从皇上<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>下出奇计，以及<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，与皇上从容谈论<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>大事的地方很多，不是关乎<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>存亡的，所以不记载。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>于是说：\"我家世代做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>相，等到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>，不惜万<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>的家产，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>向强大的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>报仇，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>震动。如今凭<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三寸</span>之舌做帝王的老师，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>食<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>，位至<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，这是平民的极致，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">良（张良）</span>已足够了。愿舍弃人间事，想从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赤松子</span>游历罢了。\"于是学习辟穀、导引、轻身之术。正逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>感激<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>，就强迫他进食，说：\"人生<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一世</span>之间，如白驹过隙，何至于自苦到这种地步呢！\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>不得已，勉强听从而进食。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八年</span>后去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张良\">文成侯（张良）</span>。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">不疑</span>继承侯爵。"
