      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">不疑</span>，孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>因不敬获罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
